  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示三个分支的复杂合并场景。主线叫branch_m，左右各有一个分支branch_l和branch_n，最终要体现多次交叉合并。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_m",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_n",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个分支的层级关系怎么安排？branch_m作为主线，branch_l和branch_n的显示顺序有要求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mainBranchOrder",
        "order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "branch_m居中，order设为1；branch_l在左边，order为0；branch_n在右边，order为2。这样视觉上比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_m",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_n",
        "order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，分支结构已搭建。我先在branch_m上创建初始提交a，然后分出branch_l和branch_n。接下来提交怎么分配？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit a",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_n"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "branch_n先做提交u，然后切回branch_l做提交f。接着branch_m要先后合并branch_n和branch_l，形成第一次交叉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit u",
        "commit f",
        "branch_n",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_m",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成到branch_m合并两个分支的步骤。现在branch_n和branch_l各自要反向合并branch_m吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_n",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_m",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，branch_n先merge branch_m，然后branch_l也merge branch_m。之后branch_m还要再合并它们一次，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_n",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_m",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "闭环结构已完成。最后两个分支还有独立提交吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
